data.description: Welcome to 1380 Sundale Dr, Lawrenceville, GA 30046Coa rare find in the heart of Lawrenceville. This spacious and hard-to-come-by traditional Ranch offers 4 beds, 2 baths, and 1,610 sqft of comfortable living space. Nestled in a tranquil setting, this home welcomes you with a tour of the main level, starting in the spacious living room and dining area. The eat-in kitchen, with an attached practical laundry space, enhances the functionality of daily living. The tour continues in the master suite, featuring an ensuite bath and his-and-hers closets. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms and a hall bath complete the main level. Venture downstairs to the finished terrace level, which boasts a bedroom, cedar closet, office space, and a versatile rec room or family area. The deck overlooks the backyard and a convenient outbuilding. Explore the nearby parks, schools, and local amenities, creating a well-rounded and convenient living experience. This home is a must-see, offering a perfect blend of traditional charm and modern comfort in Lawrenceville.
